query:
SELECT pi.id, pi.propertyId, pi.url, pi.fileKey, pi.isMain, p.title, p.companyId 
FROM property_images pi 
JOIN properties p ON pi.propertyId = p.id 
WHERE p.id = 150001 OR pi.propertyId = 150001
LIMIT 10;
